            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "```vim\r\nset statusline=%1*%{winnr()}\\ %*%<\\ %f\\ %h%m%r%=%l,%c%V\\ (%P)\r\nset lazyredraw\r\nsetlocal winbar=(winbar)\r\ncall nvim_input(':<Esc>')\r\n```",
